show.description: Thrust into power after a devastating car crash claims his father and brothers, 25-year-old Luca Marcini unexpectedly inherits the mantle of don of the notorious Marcini crime family. Written off by rivals and family members alike as too young and inexperienced to lead, Luca faces challenges from every direction as the criminal underworld watches and waits for him to fail. As Luca navigates betrayal, power struggles, and his own moral boundaries, he's determined to prove every doubter wrong—no matter how high the body count rises. Witness the birth of a new kind of mafia lord who will either transform the family legacy or be consumed by it.
